										</td>
									</tr>
								</table>
							</td>
							<td width="180">
								<table style="color: #000; font: 11px/20px helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: left;" width="100%">
									<tr valign="top">
										<td>
											<%= image_tag("http://#{@daily_deal.publisher.daily_deal_host}/themes/#{@publisher.label}/images/graphics/info.png", :alt => "Twitter", :border => '0') %>
										</td>
										<td>
											<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
												<li><a style="color: #000; text-decoration: none;" href="<%= "http://" + @daily_deal.publisher.daily_deal_host + about_us_publisher_daily_deals_path(@publisher) + "?utm_source=daily-deal-blast&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=daily-deal-blast" %>">About Us</a></li>
				                <li><a style="color: #000; text-decoration: none;" href="<%= "http://" + @daily_deal.publisher.daily_deal_host + privacy_policy_publisher_daily_deals_path(@publisher) + "?utm_source=daily-deal-blast&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=daily-deal-blast" %>">Privacy Policy</a></li>
												<li><a style="color: #000; text-decoration: none;" href="<%= "http://" + @daily_deal.publisher.daily_deal_host + terms_publisher_daily_deals_path(@publisher) + "?utm_source=daily-deal-blast&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=daily-deal-blast" %>">Terms</a></li>
											</ul>
										</td>
										<td>
											<ul style="list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
												<li><a style="color: #000; text-decoration: none;" href="<%= "http://" + @daily_deal.publisher.daily_deal_host + faqs_publisher_daily_deals_path(@publisher) + "?utm_source=daily-deal-blast&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=daily-deal-blast" %>">FAQ</a></li>
												<li><a style="color: #000; text-decoration: none;" href="<%= "http://" + @daily_deal.publisher.daily_deal_host + how_it_works_publisher_daily_deals_path(@publisher) + "?utm_source=daily-deal-blast&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=daily-deal-blast" %>">How It Works</a></li>
												<li><a style="color: #000; text-decoration: none;" href="<%= "http://" + @daily_deal.publisher.daily_deal_host + contact_publisher_daily_deals_path(@publisher) + "?utm_source=daily-deal-blast&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=daily-deal-blast" %>">Contact Us</a></li>
											</ul>
										</td>
									</tr>
								</table>
